      • maxTransition

        public org.asoem.greyfish.utils.space.Point2D maxTransition(org.asoem.greyfish.utils.space.Point2D origin,
                                                            org.asoem.greyfish.utils.space.Point2D destination)
        Get the location of the transition from origin to destination respecting collision with walls. So, if there is no wall between origin and destination that this method returns destination. Otherwise it returns the first Point2D at which the line from origin to destination intersects with a wall of any crossing tile.
        Parameters:
        origin - The origin of the transition
        destination - The destination of the transition
        Returns:
        The point of the first collision, or destination if none occurs
